title: Mozart Overtures Rinaldo Alessandrini
description:
This is Rinaldo Alessandrini's first recording with an orchestra playing on modern instruments. he is principal guest conductor with the Norwegian National Opera Orchestra. 

- With this orchestra Rinaldo Alessandrini has performed many symphonic and operatic works by Mozart; this CD is the result of that partnership 

- A program of Mozart overtures, performed with the specific touch and vision of Rinaldo Alessandrini - he succeeds in finding just the right balance between the operatic and the symphonic aspects of these overtures
